Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.83,0:00:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eyes on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}We are F/ACE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo, E/YES!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.88,0:00:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahagia dan cantik,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.09,0:00:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku malaikatmu, Natsuki Ishibashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, apa acara kita hari ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini ruang konseling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tempat kalian bisa menanyakan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asisten kali ini adalah…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hadir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ori.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senang bertemu kalian hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}E/YES yang punya masalah kali ini adalah
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}murid SMA yang tinggal di Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Uhomi Uhoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku. Aku tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita lanjutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.54,0:00:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Baru-baru ini aku menyukai seseorang."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Tapi orang itu menyukai orang lain."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Haruskah aku menyatakan perasaanku?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perasaan Uhouhomi saat ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebenarnya sangatlah berharga.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika menyatakan perasaan\Nbisa membuatmu lega melupakannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin itu patut dicoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, jika tidak,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau tidak perlu terburu-buru\Nmenyatakan perasaanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja, kau juga tak bisa diam saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ajak dia bicara dan tunjukkan\Nbetapa memesonanya dirimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.07,0:01:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ori, kau punya saran?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.74,0:01:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutku,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natsuki benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan mudah menyerah.\NBuatlah dia memperhatikanmu terlebih dahulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti yang kalian dengar,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}wali kelas kalian, Bu Tanaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sedang cuti melahirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sebagai asisten wali kelas\Nakan menggantikannya mulai sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Namaku Asuka Inoue.\N- Asuka akan jadi wali kelas kita?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.02,0:03:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mohon kerja samanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asyik!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panggil aku "Bu Guru".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat bersemangat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu Inoue adalah guru baru\Nyang pindah ke sini tahun ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Dia selalu baik kepada semua orang.\N- Cara pakainya sama seperti dahulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takahashi, kau lupa\Nmengerjakan PR lagi, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai besok, kau harus ikut\Nkelas bimbingan pagi selama sepekan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Namun, dia sangat tegas pada pemalas.\N- Apa? Berlebihan sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Untung aku kerjakan PR-ku.\N- Ini sama sekali tidak berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Jika harus ikut kelas bimbingan,\N- Jika kau tidak mau ikut,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- aku tidak bisa pergi\N- kumpulkan PR-mu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- kerja paruh waktu.\N- Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dah. Sampai besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini, aku juga akan berjuang\Ndemi biasku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}handuk mini eksklusif\Nanggota klub penggemar F/ACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bias kita sama atau tidak?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasku merah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasku kuning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau juga E/YES?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon memang luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, seleraku agak membosankan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa, aku paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski Tamon bukan biasmu,\Nsemua orang pasti menyukai wajahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bias Ibu adalah Natsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia manis sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia selalu mengutarakan isi pikirannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini rasanya agak aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi karena itu, orang-orang\Nmenganggapnya terlalu keras kepala.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski tidak terlihat,\Nsebenarnya dia itu pekerja keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya cairan pembersih sudah mau habis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan membelinya sekalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini lip gloss buatan Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bukan hanya pandai bicara,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia juga merancang produk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sungguh multitalenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin beli, tapi belum pernah\Nbelajar tata rias dengan serius.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah warna mana yang cocok untukku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ternyata benar kau.\N- Natsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita pernah bertemu\Ndi kamp pelatihan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau beli ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seleramu bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dekat sekali. Matanya sangat besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tipe Musim Semi Hangat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama sepertiku.\NWarna merah muda pasti cocok untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kebetulan aku bawa sampelnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cobalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Akan kucoba...\N- Hei, tunggu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa mengoleskannya\Nlebih tebal di bibir atas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, sudah selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkilau.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manis sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat cocok untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ambil saja untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika suka, cobalah warna yang lain juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natsuki persis seperti yang di TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia supel dan sangat ramah. Itu bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, jarak personalnya\Nsaat bicara agak aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mohon bantuannya lagi hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Tuan Suram?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku... Maaf. Kau mengejutkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah lip gloss ini cocok untukku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin aneh jika penggemar gila tak seksi\Nsepertiku tiba-tiba memakai riasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menjaga jarak dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana jika dia mengira aku merias diri\Nuntuk menarik perhatiannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon, menikahlah denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:07:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benar-benar salah menilaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal aku sudah bilang\Nhanya jadi pembantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mau dia mengira aku mencampuradukkan\Npekerjaan dan urusan pribadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong jangan mendekat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}daripada membiarkannya\Nterlalu dekat denganku,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin lebih baik sedikit berhati-hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, Tuan Suram\Ntidak bisa merasakan bahaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga ingin menjadi sepertimu\Nyang selalu ada untukku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kau salah paham, Tuan Suram.\N- Jangan mendekat. Jangan menatapku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memakai lip gloss ini\Nbukan untuk menarik perhatianmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak pernah berniat\Nmembuatmu jatuh cinta padaku,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku baru sadar,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan marah jika kau membenciku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana mungkin aku membencimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya saja, bibirmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}terlihat sangat berkilau.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terlihat seperti wanita dewasa,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi, aku agak gugup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksud pria yang tiap gerakannya\Nbisa memikat wanita dewasa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku terlihat aneh\Nmemakai lip gloss ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu cocok untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sengaja melakukan ini\Natau memang konyol?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, sepertinya aku sudah terbiasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak sengaja bertemu Natsuki\Ndi apotek tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa,\Ndia malah memakaikannya padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natsuki pasti sedang sangat sibuk sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti yang kau tahu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natsuki yang menulis beberapa lagu F/ACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenggat waktu lagu barunya adalah besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harusnya dia mengurung diri\Ndi kamar hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kalian lihat Natsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baru saja melihatnya di luar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia kabur lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bolos latihan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bahkan mengabaikan pekerjaannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia juga belum mengembalikan uang\Nyang dia pinjam!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bisa memaafkannya lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bantu cari dia juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kalian menemukannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seret saja dia kemari!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepalaku sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku terlalu banyak minum semalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh tidak mau bekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat atas kemenanganmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami berlarian di jalanan malam hari\Nuntuk mencari Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau melihatnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidak ada di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menemukannya. Itu Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya kami berhasil menemukannya, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamar ini kotor sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cukup, Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia Natsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat aku bertemu dengannya di apotek,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}matanya tampak dua kali lebih besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa aku harus menulis lagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suruh saja profesional yang melakukannya.\NMenyebalkan sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan minum saat aku sedang memarahimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Shiraishi sangat menghargai bakatmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menulisnya\Nhanya karena tak ada anggaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau membohongi siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan omong kosongmu. Tulis saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mau. Aku membencimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu pantas dikatakan\Npada penagih utangmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kembali bekerja, Perokok!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau melihat sisi buruk kami lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah terbiasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natsuki ternyata punya sisi tersembunyi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hanya sedikit kecanduan merokok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia suka minum dan bermain pachinko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bukan orang jahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setidaknya begitu menurutku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sangat mengkhawatirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}anggota kami lagi.\NKami membuatmu mencemaskan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, benarkah ini tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kau sudah terlibat, aku akan jujur.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, ini bisa terjadi lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, kami akan meluncurkan\Nacara TV dengan nama kami tahun depan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keito.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita sangat terkejut\Nhingga membentur plafon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang harus kita lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepalamu tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh kulanjutkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natsuki bertanggung jawab
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atas lagu tema acara itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Nkita akan mendengar lagu Natsuki lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, Natsuki\Nsama sekali tidak termotivasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya dia memang tidak ikut\Nlatihan tambahan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dia terus bermalas-malasan\Nhingga membuat semua orang khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini acara TV pertama dengan nama kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}E/YES juga sudah lama menantikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin melakukan yang terbaik.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, dengan kondisi Natsuki saat ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kesenjangan antusiasme antaranggota\Nmemang menjadi masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, orang itu sangat sulit dihadapi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, aku harus ke toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau keterlaluan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia telanjang dada!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memalukan sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakai bajumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ruangan itu tidak ada AC-nya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, cepat tulis lagunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutmu wajahku terlihat berbeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus membentuknya seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitulah. Aku tidak operasi plastik.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mataku hanya lelah seiring waktu,\Njadi, aku tidak memakainya saat sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau pipis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jaga ucapanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa F/ACE akan kena masalah lagi\Nkarena anggota yang tidak akur?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mengumumkan hasilnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tema Festival Budaya Kelas 2-A
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah kedai makanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Bagus!\N- Asyik!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi hari ini, kita akan membahas menu\Ndan membagi tugas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita memasak bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Utage pintar memasak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setuju. Ayo kita daftar Tim Dapur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mau daftar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, Kinoshita,\Nkau ketua Tim Dapur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa? Aku?\N- pasti bisa, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Mari kita berjuang bersama.\N- Dia sangat cocok.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum pernah menjadi ketua\Nseumur hidupku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, hidupku sangat tenang\Nsebelum bertemu Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, karena sudah ditunjuk,\Naku harus melakukan yang terbaik.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku ini ketuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau terlihat sangat serius?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga terkejut\Nmelihat foto resmi baru Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penampilannya terlihat kurang bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedang memikirkan apa yang harus\Ndijual di Festival Budaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang klise,\Ntapi bagaimana dengan takoyaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ide bagus. Kutulis dahulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, keluargaku juga\Nmenjual takoyaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menu yang paling populer\Nadalah takoyaki keju.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Isinya keju, bukan gurita.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu masih bisa disebut takoyaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, kedengarannya lezat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang tuaku
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membuat ini untuk temanku\Nyang kesulitan uang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, murid-murid di sekitar sini\Nmulai menyukainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bisa menekan biaya,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan keju sepertinya cocok dipadukan\Ndengan bahan-bahan lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kusarankan kalian mencobanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan asal kumpulkan lagunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau kurang termotivasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau tidak punya bakat,\Nkau punya apa lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tulis ulang jika kau tak mau\Nmenurunkan reputasi F/ACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedang apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf karena muncul tiba-tiba di depanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, aku agak khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentang acara baru itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski aku tidak bisa menulisnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mereka akan meminta orang lain menulisnya\Natau memakai lagu yang sudah ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka tak akan membatalkan acara\Nkarena hal sepele. Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mencemaskanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya kau melakukan segalanya\Ndengan mudah,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kali ini kau tampak kesulitan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau belum pernah seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak apa-apa.\NAku hanya sedang tidak termotivasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga tahu tema acara itu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa muda, tantangan, dan tangis haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya tidak suka tema seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa aku mengerti maksudmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asal kau tahu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kukira kau hanya memedulikan dirimu sendiri\Ndan tidak peduli pada orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak kusangka kau begitu perhatian.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, kau berubah belakangan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa pola pikirmu berubah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pola pikirku?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin bisa dibilang...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:17:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku terpengaruh oleh seseorang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku datang bukan untuk membicarakan diriku,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku malah terus mengoceh tanpa malu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku jadi termotivasi sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih atas perhatianmu.\NAku akan berusaha sebaik mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitulah ceritanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bilang akan berusaha sebaik mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya. Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempo hari kau bilang,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jika aku membencimu, kau akan marah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Artinya sesuai dengan apa yang kukatakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang takut dibenci\Natau mengecewakan orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu masuk akal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan membersihkan kamar mandi sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:17:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}alasanku itu sama sekali tidak masuk akal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tidak mau Tuan Suram membenciku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan kata lain, aku ingin dia menyukaiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Inilah awal dari pemikiran paling berbahaya\Nyang seharusnya tidak kumiliki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku. Apa yang telah kulakukan\Npada aset berharga negara ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan coba mengelak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mendengar gumamanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Coba ulangi perkataanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Telingaku! Telingaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengekspos perasaanku di depan Tamon\Nyang seharusnya kuhormati
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah tindakan tidak sopan\Nyang tak bisa kuulangi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini menyangkut harga diriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau memaksaku mengatakannya lagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lebih baik aku gigit lidah dan mati saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memikirkannya saja sudah membuatku malu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong jangan memaksaku lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, aku sangat bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira akhirnya kau menyingkirkan logikamu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan bersedia mengutarakan isi hatimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah sebabnya aku tak bisa melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau dengar lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kubilang, jika kau memaksaku,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lebih baik aku gigit lidah dan mati saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perasaan ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sedang mempermainkan hatiku
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dengan berkata seperti itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Darkhara?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau dengar lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau tidak mau mati demi sampah sepertiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Utage Kinoshita, 16 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:20:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Natsuki menghilang lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cari dia dan bawa kembali\Nke apartemen sekarang juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lezat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasa mochi keju ini pasti sangat populer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus berterima kasih pada Bu Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku tak mengerti\N- Dia bahkan meminjamkan pemanggang
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- diriku lagi.\N- dan membantu memikirkan resepnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelumnya, selama Tamon\Nhidup sehat di dunia ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku sudah puas mendukungnya diam-diam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Namun sekarang, hatiku\N- Biarkan Bu Asuka
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- merasakan sesuatu\N- mencobanya juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- yang belum pernah kurasakan sebelumnya.\N- Bagaimana menurutmu, Utage?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ini fakta yang tak terbantahkan.\N- Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.01,0:20:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Meski begitu...\N- Utage?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mendengarkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan mengarang cerita fiksi\Nsaat sedang makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mendengarkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.61,0:20:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau meminta Bu Asuka mencicipinya?\NAku akan memanggilnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, berhenti!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhentilah melawan,\Ndasar pria mencurigakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu Asuka, kau tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:20:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kinoshita.\N- Hei, tunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tolong telepon polisi sekarang.\N- Hei, dengarkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berhasil menangkap orang mencurigakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kubilang tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini aku, Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memanggilnya "Asuka"...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian saling mengenal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitulah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum pernah melihatnya.\NAku tidak mengenalnya sama sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin Gen Z tahu tentang F/ACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku tidak terlalu mengenal mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena ponselku
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Bahkan jika mereka\N- jatuh ke kolam 10 tahun yang lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- baru bertemu,\N- Kau
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- bukankah Ibu penggemar Natsuki?\N- pembohong yang payah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus kembali bekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.42,0:21:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita, aku akan kembali ke kelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, kau ceroboh sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa jadi guru yang menelantarkan murid\Nbersama pria mencurigakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitukah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:22:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian saling mengenal, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Haruskah kubilang iya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.65,0:22:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mantan pacarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.28,0:22:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mantan pacar...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.99,0:22:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mantan pacar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.87,0:22:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mantan pacar?!
